CHEVRON HOLDS 100 PERCENT OF

THE COMMON STOCK ISSUED BY CHEVRON SOUTH AFRICA (PTY) LIMITED,

WHICH OWNS THE CAPE TOWN REFINERY. A CONSORTIUM OF SOUTH AFRICAN

