ITEM 7A.    QUANTITATIVE

AND QUALITATIVE DISCLOSURES ABOUT MARKET RISK

THE COMPANYS DISCUSSION OF INTEREST RATE, FOREIGN CURRENCY

AND COMMODITY PRICE MARKET RISK IS CONTAINED IN

