(FAS 143). UNDER FAS 143, THE FAIR

VALUE OF A LIABILITY FOR AN ASSET RETIREMENT

OBLIGATION IS RECORDED WHEN THERE IS A LEGAL

OBLIGATION ASSOCIATED WITH THE RETIREMENT OF

